    {
        "content": "<p>cfallin <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13953#issuecomment-5070747847\">commented</a> on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13953\">PR #13953</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Ah, yeah, sorry, I should've registered that here -- brain saw wildcard -&gt; wildcard and I missed that. Thanks; @dev-er1 we'll close this as above.</p>\n</blockquote>",
